Package org.wmn4j.notation.access

Interface PartIterator

All Superinterfaces:
Iterator<Measure>
public interface PartIterator extends Iterator<Measure>
Iterator for iterating through the measures in a part. The measures are iterated in their temporal order, i.e., the order of measure numbers. For parts with multiple staves the measures with the same number are iterated starting from the staff with the smallest number. Does not support removing.

Instances of this class are not thread-safe.
